{\Large \bf Lectures on D-branes, tachyon condensation, and string
  field theory
\\}
\vspace{3mm}

\end{center}
\vspace{0.2in}

\begin{center}
Notes on lectures presented at the CECS School on Quantum Gravity,\\
Valdivia, Chile, January 2002

\end{center}



\vspace{7 mm}

\begin{center}

Washington Taylor

\vspace{3mm}
{\small \sl Center for Theoretical Physics} \\
{\small \sl MIT, Bldg.  6-308} \\
